html(lang='en')
  head
    style.
      .btn {
      background-color: #2ab3f6;
      border: none;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 15px;
      text-align: center;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), 0 6px 20px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.19);
      border-radius: 15px;
      font-size: 16px;
      }
      .boarder{
      max-width: 600px;
      padding: 1rem;
      position: relative;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #28b3f6, #2ab3f6, #708ae8);
      padding: 20px;
      }
      .box{
      background: #FFFFFF;
      color: black;
      padding: 2rem;
      }
      .logo {
      max-width: 40%;
      height: auto;
      padding-bottom: 0px;
      }
      .title{
      color : #0000A0;
      font-size: 200%;
      }
      .middle{
      color : #FFC502;
      font-size: 150%;
      }
      .bottom{
      color : #000000;
      font-size: 120%;
      display: inline-block;
      }
      table {
      font-family: arial, sans-serif;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      width: 100%;
      }
      td, th {
      border: 1px solid #dddddd;
      text-align: left;
      padding: 8px;
      }
      tr:nth-child(even) {
      background-color: #dddddd;
      }
      tr:nth-child(odd) {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      }
  body
    .boarder
      .box
        center
          img.logo(src='https://ionbahamas.org/js/react/src/imgs/logo.jpg')
          div.title Ion Bahamas Monthly Report 
        p
          | Dear 
        p
          | Welcome to the Igniting Our Nation Bahamas Non-Profit Organization. You are now an inducted ION Bahamas member. Payment for your membership enrollment has been successful.
        p
          | Our mission is to be of assistance to, and enhance the lives of Bahamians and friends of The Bahamas, both at home and abroad via educational and civic engagement.  Please take the time to browse our website. Should you have any additional questions we may be contacted at info@ionbahamas.org. Thank you for joining our community. We welcome you to visit us on 
          a(href='https://www.facebook.com/ION-Bahamas-101203231240251') Facebook
          | .
        p Regards,
        p
          | Carlisle Mott
          br
          | President
        table
          tbody
            tr
              th Order Details
              th Product
              th Status
            tr
              td
                div Date : 
                div Amount : 
                div Card Type : 
                div Last 4 : 
              td 1-Year(s) Membership
              td 
        br
        table
          tbody
            tr
              th Name
              th Email
              th Amount
              th Cause
              th Date Donated
            - for (var i = 0; i < monthlyDonations.length ; i++) {
              tr
                td #{monthlyDonations[i].FName} #{monthlyDonations[i].vName}
                td #{monthlyDonations[i].Email}
                td #{monthlyDonations[i].Amount}
                td #{monthlyDonations[i].Cause}
                td #{monthlyDonations[i].date_donated}
            - }
        br
        center
          a(href=`${membersData.result.payment.receipt_url}`).btn Download receipt
